uk.co.strangeskies.utilities.flowcontrol

Interface StripedReadWriteLockRelease<K>

  • Type Parameters:
    K - The type of the keys used to index into the locks.
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    StripedReadWriteLock<K>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LimitedReadWriteLockReleaseWrapper, StripedReadWriteLockImpl

    public interface StripedReadWriteLockRelease<K>
    An interface exposing part of the functionality of a StripedReadWriteLock. This interface allows clients to release locks, but not to obtain them or wait for them.
